description: For weeks, Deathstroke has fought to learn the identity of the person manipulating him from the shadows – the person who sent him the briefcase and created the Legacy identity. Now, Slade will face this threat head on as an important figure from his past returns with a vengeance. Throw everything you thought you knew about Slade Wilson out the window, because everything changes after this issue’s unbelievable battle!
name: Deadly Reunions

description: Hunted through the streets of Gotham City, her former teammates on the Suicide Squad in relentless pursuit – Harley Quinn is out of friends, out of luck and out of time. Will Harley find The Joker before the Squad finds her? Place your bets, people: It’s Harley Quinn vs. the Suicide Squad! Plus: Harley’s origin revealed – it ain’t pretty!
name: The Hunt for Harley Quinn, Conclusion

description: The Necrosha event hits X-Men: Legacy! Selene's master plan is clicking into place, but she got something she didn't plan for when Destiny was brought back to life. A major X-villain snuck back into the world of the living along with Destiny, and now a who's who of X-Men are being sent to Muir Island to deal with their resurrected foe. Join Nightcrawler, Colossus, Psylocke, Rogue and the X-Men's newest member - the master of magnetism, Magneto - as they dive into Necrosha. Collecting X-MEN LEGACY #231-234 and material from X-NECROSHA.
name: X-Men Legacy: Necrosha

description: Guest-starring MIDNIGHTER! A voice is calling from the Himalayas; a dark secret awaits Grifter. He tracks it down, only to discover that the secret has a protector: Midnighter, who must not allow Grifter to leave the mountains alive. A massive battle on treacherous ice slopes shows Grifter that he’s in a world of heroes he cannot defeat and opens him up to new world-changing secrets as deadly as they are powerful.
name: Frostbite

description: An immortal villain named The Inquisitor enacts his plan to bring hell to Earth, starting in Barcelona. Luckily for the city (and the rest of the world), the Shade happens to be in town… Don’t miss out on a series that MTV Geek calls “a perfect comic book”!
name: Las Cinco Esquinas

description: Martin receives a book about Atlantis and Mu, and especially about Adam, the obscure founder of the Men in Black.
name: La città dei cinque anelli

description: The final conflict between The Ray and the evil maestro who has been behind all his woes comes to a conclusion. Lucien will need to take his powers to an all-new level to defeat the evil Director and his reality warping abilities.
name: Part Four

description: While searching to find the second part of the book about the war between Atlantis and Mu, Martin discovers several reports of an alleged UFO crash occurred in 1896.
name: UFO 1896

description: The siege on S.H.A.D.E. City comes to a bloody conclusion, and it may mean the end of the Creature Commandos! With the Hub under Humanid control and Nina’s evil monsters staging a coup, S.H.A.D.E. headquarters is in total disarray. But nothing can prepare Frankenstein for the terrible secret that lies beneath it all!
name: The Siege of S.H.A.D.E. City, Part Two

description: BRAND-NEW ARC! GREAT JUMPING-ON POINT FOR NEW READERS! The source of the imbalance of Law and Chaos that’s been assaulting the Multiverse is revealed, and it will leave Moorcock fans reeling! Finally, all incarnations of the Eternal Champion will have to join together to fight against forces bigger than Law and Chaos, for the very survival of existence itself!
A fiery menace is turning the city into an inferno, and only Lobster Johnson and his league of crime fighters can put an end to these paranormal horrors.
name: 3 (of 5)

description:
Death has come for Conan and his fellow sailors in the visage of the privateer Bêlit! Rage and desire mingle in an orgy of slaughter as the barbarian and the pirate queen glimpse each other for the first time--as opponents in a battle to the last man!

Number 89 in a series.
name: Queen of the Black Coast, Part 2

description: In this epic from issues #37-41, a foot soldier called Mads gives us a grunt's-eye view of the Siege of Paris, where hundreds defended against thousands, and political maneuvering was as important as the clash of the shield wall.
name: Vol. 6

description: The theft of an essential component for the production of hydrogen bombs is intertwined with the mysterious disappearance of the Italian physicist Ettore Majorana, in 1938. The telepaths of the Altrove base have picked up a message that seems to come from the same Majorana. The message announces a terrible calamity that only Martin Mystère will be able to prevent.
name: Il caso Majorana

description: Oliver Mac Dermott, with the help of Martin Mystère and Java, has to resolve ten enigmas, hidden in the same number of European cities. The final objective is to be able to come into possession of the inheritance left by his bizarre uncle Archie. It would be a simple treasure hunt if two relatives of Oliver’s, interested in the failure of his mission, were not secretly following their footsteps.
name: La pista cifrata

description: Martin, along with Java, travels to Bombay for a newspaper report. During his stay in India is prone to severe amnesia, which he can not understand the cause.
name: La pietra di Jivaka

description: The countdown that will take us to the end of 1999 continues, the conclusion of the Indian adventure reveals the nature of the stone of Jivaka, while Martin has a terrible vision of the future that could happen. But Mystère also faces much more immediate danger: in Washington, he becomes aware of a secret that has already killed a man and traces back to a mysterious criminal organization.
name: L'isola delle rose

description: A formidable weapon that can unleash devastating earthquakes at a distance has been achieved starting from the scientific discoveries of Nikola Tesla, and is currently in the hands of a crazy secret society whose purpose is to unleash a total war. From a secret base in Alaska, the organization is about to experience the powerful instrument of death, and only Martin Mystère may be able to stop it.
name: La terra trema!

description: A surreal adventure in constant balance between fantasy and reality. A young writer recalls the restless spirit of an actress of the thirties, who committed suicide. This forces the girl to write novels that allow to the restless soul to live again...
name: L'albergo sulla scogliera
